All Music Album Review (by Heather Phares):

20 Greatest Hits collects the most memorable songs from Tommy Roe, Gary Puckett, and Dennis Yost & the Classics IV. Puckett's "Woman, Woman," "Young Girl," and "Lady Willpower" are included on the album, along with Yost's "Traces," "Stormy," and "Every Day With You Girl." Tommy Roe's "Sheila," "Crimson and Clover," and "Dizzy" help complete this entertaining retrospective.
